  heading: Electrical Lab
  details: 'An electrical lab is a workspace where students perform experiments on
    electrical circuits and components.

    It is equipped with power supplies,
    meters, and instruments to measure voltage, current, and resistance.

    The
    lab helps learners understand practical applications of electrical and electronic
    theories.'
